{"id":1167,"text":"#Causes - Dacryoadenitis - 1D80.Y\nThe causes of lacrimal gland inflammation may be classified as: Infectious, Idiopathic, Autoimmune, Lymphoproliferative. Infectious dacryoadenitis: It may be: Viral dacryoadenitis: Viral dacryoadenitis is more common than bacterial, particularly in children and young adults. Bacterial dacryoadenitis: Acute suppurative bacterial dacryoadenitis is less common. Fungal dacryoadenitis: It is rare and may be caused by: Histoplasmosis. Blastomycosis. Protozoal dacryoadenitis: It may rarely be caused by organisms like acanthamoeba. Idiopathic dacryoadenitis: Idiopathic is a nonspecific dacryoadenitis and is the most common histopathological diagnosis made for the lacrimal gland lesions. Autoimmune dacryoadenitis: The lacrimal gland is often affected by autoimmune disorders and may be the first or only presentation. Lymphoproliferative dacryoadenitis: Lymphoproliferative tumours may also cause orbital and lacrimal gland inflammation. ","entities":[{"id":16762,"label":"Diagnosis_E","start_offset":657,"end_offset":684},{"id":16734,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":10,"end_offset":24},{"id":16735,"label":"Complication_E","start_offset":48,"end_offset":75},{"id":16737,"label":"Cause_E","start_offset":110,"end_offset":120},{"id":16743,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":310,"end_offset":334},{"id":16744,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":336,"end_offset":378},{"id":16745,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":395,"end_offset":416},{"id":16748,"label":"Cause_E","start_offset":467,"end_offset":480},{"id":16751,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":508,"end_offset":511},{"id":16754,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":619,"end_offset":634},{"id":16755,"label":"Complication_E","start_offset":698,"end_offset":720},{"id":16756,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":722,"end_offset":747},{"id":16761,"label":"Complication_E","start_offset":932,"end_offset":971},{"id":16736,"label":"Cause_E","start_offset":98,"end_offset":108},{"id":16738,"label":"Cause_E","start_offset":122,"end_offset":132},{"id":16739,"label":"Cause_E","start_offset":134,"end_offset":153},{"id":16740,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":155,"end_offset":180},{"id":16741,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":193,"end_offset":213},{"id":16742,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":215,"end_offset":235},{"id":16746,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":418,"end_offset":421},{"id":16747,"label":"Cause_E","start_offset":451,"end_offset":465},{"id":16749,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":482,"end_offset":506},{"id":16752,"label":"Cause_E","start_offset":535,"end_offset":562},{"id":16753,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":564,"end_offset":589},{"id":16757,"label":"Anatomy_E","start_offset":749,"end_offset":767},{"id":16758,"label":"Complication_E","start_offset":789,"end_offset":809},{"id":16759,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":853,"end_offset":887},{"id":16760,"label":"Cause_E","start_offset":889,"end_offset":916}],"relations":[{"id":8106,"from_id":16746,"to_id":16747,"type":"caused_by_R"},{"id":8107,"from_id":16734,"to_id":16748,"type":"caused_by_R"},{"id":8108,"from_id":16751,"to_id":16752,"type":"caused_by_R"},{"id":8109,"from_id":16754,"to_id":16762,"type":"has_diagnosis_R"},{"id":8111,"from_id":16758,"to_id":16757,"type":"influence_R"},{"id":8113,"from_id":16759,"to_id":16761,"type":"has_complication_R"},{"id":8110,"from_id":16754,"to_id":16755,"type":"has_complication_R"}],"Comments":[]}
{"id":1168,"text":"#Symptoms - Dacryoadenitis - 1D80.Y\nSymptoms at presentation depend upon whether the disease process is acute or chronic. Acute dacryoadenitis: It may present acutely with: Swelling of the lateral third of the upper lid, Pain in the lid with associated feeling of pressure in the eye, Redness of the lid, Conjunctival swelling, Conjunctival redness, Mucopurulent discharge from the eye, Swelling of the lymph nodes (submandibular), Bulging of the eyeball, Downward and inward displacement of the globe, Difficulty in eye movements. Chronic dacryoadenitis: It may show: Enlarged lacrimal gland which is mobile. Mild to severe features of dry eye.\n\n","entities":[{"id":17093,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":12,"end_offset":26},{"id":17094,"label":"Complication_E","start_offset":104,"end_offset":120},{"id":17097,"label":"Symptom_E","start_offset":173,"end_offset":219},{"id":17099,"label":"Symptom_E","start_offset":285,"end_offset":303},{"id":17101,"label":"Symptom_E","start_offset":328,"end_offset":348},{"id":17102,"label":"Symptom_E","start_offset":350,"end_offset":385},{"id":17103,"label":"Symptom_E","start_offset":387,"end_offset":430},{"id":17104,"label":"Symptom_E","start_offset":432,"end_offset":501},{"id":17106,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":532,"end_offset":554},{"id":17095,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":122,"end_offset":142},{"id":17096,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":144,"end_offset":147},{"id":17098,"label":"Symptom_E","start_offset":221,"end_offset":283},{"id":17100,"label":"Symptom_E","start_offset":305,"end_offset":326},{"id":17105,"label":"Symptom_E","start_offset":503,"end_offset":530},{"id":17107,"label":"Disease_E","start_offset":556,"end_offset":559},{"id":17108,"label":"Symptom_E","start_offset":569,"end_offset":608},{"id":17109,"label":"Symptom_E","start_offset":610,"end_offset":644}],"relations":[{"id":8298,"from_id":17095,"to_id":17097,"type":"has_symptom_R"},{"id":8299,"from_id":17095,"to_id":17098,"type":"has_symptom_R